<!-- Problem -->
<section class="section-centered">
  <div class="section-label slide-left">The Problem</div>
  <h2 class="section-title slide-left">Your business is leaking information<br>you don't know about</h2>
  <p class="section-sub slide-left">Attackers spend hours researching targets before striking. Most businesses have no idea what's visible from the outside until it's too late.</p>
  <div class="problem-grid">
    <div class="problem-card danger slide-left">
      <div class="icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Email Spoofing Risk</h3>
      <p>Missing DMARC records let anyone send emails that look like they're from your company — enabling phishing attacks on your customers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card danger slide-left">
      <div class="icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="7.5" cy="15.5" r="5.5"/><path d="m21 2-9.6 9.6"/><path d="m15.5 7.5 3 3L22 7l-3-3"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Leaked Credentials</h3>
      <p>Breached email and password combinations from past data breaches are freely available online and actively used to break into business accounts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card danger slide-right">
      <div class="icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2"/><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="6" y2="6"/><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="18" y2="18"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Exposed Infrastructure</h3>
      <p>Forgotten subdomains, dev servers, and open database ports are indexed publicly and routinely scanned by automated bots.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card danger slide-right">
      <div class="icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Lookalike Domains</h3>
      <p>Typosquatted domains (e.g. acme-corp.com vs acmecorp.com) are registered by attackers for phishing campaigns targeting your brand.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section id="how-it-works" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border-radius: 20px; max-width: 100%; padding: 80px 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;" class="section-centered">
    <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to full visibility</h2>
