        <h3>BotStop Scans</h3>
        <p>200+ passive sources are queried — DNS records, breach databases, threat feeds, SSL certs, social profiles, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step slide-right">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Get Your Report</h3>
        <p>Findings are categorized by severity with plain-English explanations and specific fix instructions for each issue.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What we find -->
